            "creation_date": 1400440793,
            "body": "<p>I personally would use an ArrayList here.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>private List&lt;Character&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;Character&gt;();\n\nint i=0;\n\nBufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new FileReader(\"pathToFile...\"));\n\nchar c = '-1';\n\nwhile (c!='\\n') {\n    list.add((char) br.read());\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Something like that.<\/p>\n",
